## Description {#details}

Typed iterator through <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mdnode">MDNode</a> operands.

An iterator that transforms an <em>MDNode::iterator</em> into an iterator over a particular <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/metadata">Metadata</a> subclass.

Definition at line 1601 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/ir/metadata-h">Metadata.h</a>.
